146
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,000
Lift the bride's veil.

147
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:29,480
Lin Xiaoxiao

148
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,519
Before I met you

149
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,399
I didn't believe I could fall in love with someone

150
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,480
Maybe I would have a business marriage

151
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,079
But I would never find love

152
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,639
Until I met you

153
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,439
That day

154
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,439
You were like that runaway jeep

155
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,519
Crashing straight into my heart

156
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,319
He

157
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,000
Is the one I love

158
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,480
You are both stubborn and brave

159
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:02,959
And strong and wild

160
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,879
Like a little chili pepper

161
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,079
You make my heart

162
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,040
Burn with passion

163
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,800
We've been through so much together

164
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,160
We faced hardships side by side

165
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,240
Even willing to sacrifice everything for each other

166
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,439
Help!

167
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:46,840
Meeting you was unexpected

168
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,200
But falling in love with you

169
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,000
